The category of presheaves \hat {C} is the free
cocompletion of C, in an appropriately weak 2-categorical sense. In
particular, for every functor C\xrightarrow {F} E with E cocomplete, there exists,
uniquely up to unique isomorphism, a cocontinuous functor
\hat {C}\to  E that extends the Yoneda embedding of C: 




